        "TileImage": "$($repository 69be3679-a4a0-4466-aff4-a44888465637).Image",
        "Description": "They wear white coats and clean smiles. They sign checks and bless inaugurations. They buy tranquility like one buys a rare wine: slowly, discreetly, and tastefully.\rBut cleanliness doesn&apos;t erase the trace they leave behind—not when someone bothers to look at the margins. The margins tell something else: packages moved at night, files annotated with an overly hasty pencil, guests who never return home.\r\rSapienza is a map that knows how to keep secrets.",
